title: Monster Truck - Furiosity
description:
Monster Truck are a Canadian rock band from Hamilton, Ontario, who have released two EPs.[1] Their album Furiosity was released on Dine Alone Records on May 28, 2013. It was distributed on Universal.[2] Members include lead singer and bassist Jon Harvey, guitarist Jeremy Widerman, keyboardist Brandon Bliss and drummer Steve Kiely.

The band won the 2013 Juno Award for Breakthrough Group of the Year.[3] They played the Download Festival in 2013 and will support Vista Chino on their European tour in October and November 2013.
